tv.amwa.maj.industry

Class WeakReferenceSet<T extends WeakReferenceTarget>

  • java.lang.Object
    • tv.amwa.maj.industry.WeakReferenceSet<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of the target of all the references in the set.

    public class WeakReferenceSet<T extends WeakReferenceTarget>
extends Object

    Represents a set of weak references and provides a means to resolve them at runtime. The class provides a consistent set of delegate add, contains and remove methods for weak reference set type properties.

    See Also:
    WeakReference, WeakReferenceTarget, WeakReferenceVector, TypeDefinitionSet, TypeDefinitionWeakObjectReference, JPAGenerator.generateORM(java.util.Collection, String)
